sentences.sentence: The unemployment rate is unacceptably high, and we have got a lot of work to do.
sentences.translation: 失业率仍然高得令人无法接受。我们还有许多工作要做。

sentences.sentence: On the other hand, if the pause time is too long, it will make the test unacceptably slow.
sentences.translation: 另一方面，如果暂停时间太长，会使得测试慢得不可接受。
